8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"57340959-37fa-949e-858d-95c0bf6c1060","name":"Note: Repack as XLSX"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Processed File (Google Drive)\n\ngoogleDrive — `upload` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Stamp Completion Time · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"dbcb0cc1-8446-bf49-a60b-c717262c8e2e","name":"Note: Archive Processed File (Google Drive)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"76b6abed-cd01-0231-65c9-6ae80edb72bc","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"53eba4fe-a950-ad0a-248e-4378f01d3a15","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Copy to Google Drive","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"c125f054-253e-f88d-d0da-b3ce7120025b","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Copy to Google Drive\n\ngoogleDrive — `upload` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Enrich with Reference Data · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"550f6121-6adb-b3dd-0ded-38526c1ac0a0","name":"Note: Archive Copy to Google Drive"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"48131e18-d8ec-468f-24c6-d68602445afe","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"3b464bdb-5028-6f43-d635-b96e2d06bb16","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow\n\nDelegates to a reusable sub-workflow (single-responsibility building block) and waits for its result.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Sub-workflow Result · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"d365c40f-7b5c-8e99-2f37-3fb3affc58af","name":"Note: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Sub-workflow Result\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Fingerprint for Idempotency","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"82dde710-aa45-633b-08d9-7b582328b9a7","name":"Note: Record Sub-workflow Result"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per asset (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"51e00d7b-6af0-db64-67ff-cd372a4ae41e","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"355f7229-96fb-45f3-a5d6-f9851d4c6de9","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"c1b8bf56-8b2b-ff2e-f1d9-ef07c93c577d","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty title","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"6f282ff6-fc6d-9320-b097-e2bf4157266e","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty title\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"3c1b6e72-e076-e920-a34e-52e2360cd325","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty title"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"977cab97-6e96-7c9f-928d-30053cebf7e6","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Sort Assets Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,520],"id":"7a979c05-e2c8-9a6f-c41f-880b08c7bd64","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Assets Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,520],"id":"cacb6ba1-e093-9f39-3283-0d68864163a0","name":"Note: Sort Assets Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7770,520],"id":"f9bc9f3c-1f24-87fd-fa40-d9f1b2ae51a5","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8094,520],"id":"8cd2d98e-26f1-51d8-5e70-dc717e8c1e3e","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8418,520],"id":"3cb85339-f703-0a47-e707-e85f59adc681","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7770,1540],"id":"610bdeda-d95c-69d1-c4c9-501fccd3d95c","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8094,1540],"id":"f14610cf-d4f8-7ddc-92f3-016c5630b997","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8418,1540],"id":"5b730631-8789-0313-0bb0-b3b9eba405c2","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Publish AI clips with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive without manual work\n\n**Pattern:** Video Production · **Level:** Architect · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nPublish AI clips with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive without manual work. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual ai video is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Download from Google Drive → Parse XLSX Contents → Clean & Reshape Rows → Rows Pass Validation? → Load Rows into Google Sheets → Repack as XLSX → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to video production without manual effort\n- Anyone automating ai video in content creation\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Responds in seconds\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"c2ee915a-acd9-f0d0-5a3c-72383b842bb9","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"5e703c27-371c-7157-6f45-668016734d79","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"6e360584-9703-1b98-59b2-9a56aa3402f2","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your ai video process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-20],"id":"b0fb1266-3b34-1bae-1adb-bb56153af8a0","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Weekly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Download from Google Drive","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Download from Google Drive":{"main":[[{"node":"Parse XLSX Contents","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Parse XLSX Contents":{"main":[[{"node":"Clean & Reshape Rows","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Clean & Reshape Rows":{"main":[[{"node":"Rows Pass Validation?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Rows Pass Validation?":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Rows into Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Quarantine Bad Rows","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Rows into Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Repack as XLSX","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Repack as XLSX":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Processed File (Google Drive)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Processed File (Google Drive)":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Copy to Google Drive","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Copy to Google Drive":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow":{"main":[[{"node":"Record Sub-workflow Result","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Sub-workflow Result":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty title","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty title":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Assets Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Assets Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Quarantine Bad Rows":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"504c957b-9772-49c9-95de-7dd1e878d2e4","id":"FDX10103"}